      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t找到了一个软件可以对app作出修改, 例如更改图标, 更改名称, 甚至完全移除图标而通过在拨号界面输入特定密码启动app. 参考以下链接.<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/China_irl/comments/z7kcap/%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8_%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA_%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83_%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E8%A7%84%E9%81%BF%E6%99%B6%E6%A0%BC%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/China_irl/comments/z7kcap/%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8_%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA_%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83_%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E8%A7%84%E9%81%BF%E6%99%B6%E6%A0%BC%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA/\">在安卓手机使用 [\"虚拟机\"] /[虚拟环境] 有效规避晶格查手机</a> </div>",
      "date": "2022-12-01",
